title: 3 Bedroom with Luxury Amenities! Attached Garage!
posting_body: Gated * Enclosed Backyards * Onsite Dog Park * Garages *
Located south of El Dorado Parkway, we are conveniently located to Highways 121 and 75.
Apartment home interiors offer brush nickel fixtures, plank flooring, euro-style cabinetry, mirrored closet doors, and full-size washer/dryer connections.
Take advantage of the sports club at your doorstep: pool and spa, indoor basketball and racquetball, sand and water volleyball, fitness center with Cybex equipment and HDTV and putting green.
Garages and enclosed backyards are available, as is WiFi in all common areas.
